content:
Legacy chat is scheduled for retirement on February 14, 2026, and is in maintenance mode until then. You can continue to use chat until that date, but we recommend transitioning to Messaging for In-App and Web for modernized customer communication.

Where: This change applies to Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience in all editions.

How: As of February 14, 2026, legacy chat will be removed and you canâ€™t access or use chat. To avoid service interruptions to your customers, migrate to Messaging for In-App and Web before that date.
title: Legacy Chat Retirements in Salesforce
